{
  "stem": "20021.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, we had-- there were young boys who would come to Tarnow to study in the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would be assigned to homes for guests to eat for the whole week, one meal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had those also occasionally, our share, whatever the community asked us to-- to join and do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So very often-- I wouldn't say always, but very often we had a guest for Friday night-- Friday night's meal, not for Saturday for some reason I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Friday nights mean there was a guest in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, it was mostly our family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And occasionally, there would be visits from family from other towns who would come from Gorlice and my father's family or-- you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What about Sukkos?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Sukkos, we-- we made our own sukkah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that, because this was great joy for the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You used to prepare all kinds of ornaments, eggs with colored paper cutouts and various thing, and decorate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The sukkah was supposed to be decorated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was the decoration of the sukkah which you showed off to your neighbors and friends and family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You would invite them, come to see our sukkah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we worked on those decorations many weeks and it was great fun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I enjoyed that very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the holiday, we ate in the sukkah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't easy, you know, because the sukkah wasn't very large.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we'd squeeze in and eat there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the meals were brought inside the sukkah and-- We used the balcony, which was fairly large, but not-- of course, limited, because it's a balcony.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We built the sukkah on that balcony.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Simchas Torah was great fun, because that was mostly celebrated in the synagogues, but the emphasis was on children.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
